Package: hetid
Title: Identification Through Heteroskedasticity for VFCI
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Fernando", "Duarte", , "duarte@alum.mit.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8495-6936"))
Description: Applies identification through heteroskedasticity from Lewbel
    (2012) for triangular systems to estimate the VFCI (volatility
    financial conditions index) by Tobias Adrian, Matthew DeHaven,
    Fernando Duarte and Tara Iyer.
